{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I'm looking for a familiar face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'm looking for-- I'm calling my father by name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I knew if I called dad, there was a lot of guys that called dad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I call him by name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I cannot find my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I'm getting desperate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father used to have a-- a habit where he would like clear his throat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Back in the good old days, so to speak, at home, he would go like, [CLEARS THROAT].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I hear that clearing of that throat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was music to my ears.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I knew it was my father by the way he cleared his throat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I ran to that-- to that noise of-- of clearing of the throat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I'm together with my father now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He wants to know why I am not with my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I said, this German officer told me to come on this side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So now, we are all together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "My father was with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There's a group of people that are-- the group consists of all the people from my town that made it up to that point, and people that we got to make acquaintances with in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We're all a group of familiar faces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We see the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We feel a smell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But we don't know-- we don't know what is happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's still in-- it's still in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They're bringing us in to a big building.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they're telling us all to undress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the only thing that we can take with us is our shoes and go to the next-- to another room in the building where they shave everybody's head.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
